      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the diced Thai eggplant and cook until it starts to soften, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced aji amarillo pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the heavy cream and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let cook for 15 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and serve hot."
  ],
